 {"value":
  "```lean\nLean.PostprocessTraces.countNodes : TracePostprocessor\n```\n***\nAppends the number of nodes inside each subtree to the subtree's head message. \n***\n*import Lean.PostprocessTraces.Postprocessors*",
  "kind": "markdown"}}
{"textDocument": {"uri": "file:///postprocess_traces_hover.lean"},
 "position": {"line": 20, "character": 24}}
